Class QVTRParser

java.lang.Object
  de.upb.m2m.quality.languages.qvtr.QVTRParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
de.upb.m2m.quality.parser.ILanguageParser
public class QVTRParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements de.upb.m2m.quality.parser.ILanguageParser

Provides the means to parse QVT-R files to a QVT-R-O AST model. The class builds on functionality provided by the MediniQVT framework.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Kapova et al., Sebastian Lehrig (lehrig@mail.upb.de)
